INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (59,1,'2021-09-22 11:04:52','2021-09-22 11:04:52','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ridhika started in August 2018 as an initiative to help young people learn the technical skills required to solve their own communities\' problems through technology. Our aim of creating and nurturing the next generation of innovators is rooted in creating a community of makers, creatives and leaders in various capacities. We engage students, mostly in high schools, and help teach them Coding, Design Thinking, Leadership and Entrepreneurship skills through an after-school program and an annual bootcamp. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>That being said, we know that not all our students will want to become full-time coders and we completely understand this. That is why we also include Career Development in our curriculum - helping Ridhika\'s participants learn about different careers so that they can be well-prepared in choosing the courses they would like to study at the university-level. Our participants get early exposure to career professionals in a variety of careers through an annual Career Day. This experience helps them learn how to best prepare for the career of their choice. They also learn the daily challenges of each career and this helps them make informed decisions on what to study in university. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Successful participants in Ridhika\'s blended curriculum go on to university prepared to be young leaders within their communities.  We also partner with organizations to help students gain internships and apprenticeships in fields involving technology. Some students even go on to work on their own projects post-high school! In this way, we ensure that young people are better prepared for jobs in the 21st century and are capable of ideating solutions to the problems their communities face. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Our Story','','publish','closed','closed','','our-story','','','2021-09-22 11:04:52','2021-09-22 11:04:52','',0,'http://localhost:10008/?page_id=59',0,'page','',0);
